name: Antbull Exquisite Relics #1 - Wiry & Spikes
description:
Antbulls appear in gloomy ambients. Catacombs, dungeons, terrains. Are they long forgotten creatures or remnants of a time yet to come? Notions such as time and story are always foretold by fiction, which folds ands molds realities, which are themselves modeled and unfolded through that which we call language. Art?
